Rating: 4
This is fantastic - I would double everything except the following amounts I used in my second batch that came out perfect: 3 andouille turkey links (9 oz), diced 3 spicy chicken sausage links (such as habanero and green chile-9 oz), diced 1 large fresh poblano chile 1 32-ounce can hominy in juice This will make a perfect consistency and plenty of sausage without it being overkill.

